{"tid":2005765,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句勵志嘅句子","createTime":"2020-05-07T10:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T04:51:22.000Z","uid":18279,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2c30257403389178e457ec09e4e667bc96aae8","tid":2005765,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"相信各位呢一年都經歷左好多困難，我想開一個認真嘅post鼓勵一下大家，大家都留低一兩句聽過勵志既說話。<br />\n<br />\n如果已經返緊工既人:<br />\n三十歲時買到三歲那年想買的玩具，八十歲時買到十八那年想得的初戀，你會明白夢想要及時實現，快樂要趁青春去追。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係熱戀中既朋友:<br />\n有時候你會期望你有驚天動地、可歌可泣的愛情故事，但多數最終能走到最後的，都係別人不予厚望的一對。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係讀緊書既朋友:<br />\n上帝永遠不會直接給予你所祈求的，而祂往往給予你得到那樣東西的機會。當你盡力去、努力去捉緊機會，你會得到上帝所應許。<br />\n<br />\n有一句比同路人:<br />\n世界只有一個，若你不想你討厭的人擁有這個世界，你就要變更強、更善良，還有不要成為當初你所討厭的人。<br />\n<br />\n另外有一句係告魯夫講:<br />\n我若是想捧大力神盃，我恨不得小組賽就碰上德國、巴西。<br />\n<br />\n可能有啲中二病加矯情，但希望可以激勵到你"},{"pid":"c9247b9c8df4f931df60741448f50f83ac57819f","tid":2005765,"uid":342563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"thx OP, my turn:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.narvii.com/image/srkyzmjupihjur3sjfheoew7ou4mpm5o_hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.narvii.com%2Fimage%2Fsrkyzmjupihjur3sjfheoew7ou4mpm5o_hq.jpg&h=71e03bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32ce91424cee5a864c0f023f156833ba779e74d6","tid":2005765,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9247b9c8df4f931df60741448f50f83ac57819f","tid":2005765,"uid":342563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"thx OP, my turn:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.narvii.com/image/srkyzmjupihjur3sjfheoew7ou4mpm5o_hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.narvii.com%2Fimage%2Fsrkyzmjupihjur3sjfheoew7ou4mpm5o_hq.jpg&h=71e03bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"蛭魔妖一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca77e6d229916e4eb1e3bff